        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，时间轴形式。我想确认一下：这个支付流程的起点是T0ms用户提交表单，终点是T1000ms用户查看确认状态，对吗？中间需要体现同步和异步两个阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T0ms",
        "T1000ms",
        "Usuario submit pago form",
        "User checks app"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，前半段是同步阻塞的，用户等待响应；后半段是异步的，涉及风控和银行回调。同步阶段大概60ms，我们要把ServiceMesh的边车延迟、Docker镜像里的JWT校验都标出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T60ms",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_DockerImage",
        "JWT validation",
        "idempotency check"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画同步段。T0ms用户提交表单，T10ms支付服务收到请求，中间插入了5ms的幂等性检查和8ms的JWT校验，这两个都挂在ServiceMesh和DockerImage上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T0ms",
        "T10ms",
        "Payment service",
        "idempotency check",
        "JWT validation",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_DockerImage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来到T25ms，这里要做余额检查和资金预留。余额查询走ServiceMesh，12ms；资金预留直接落到K8s集群，15ms。这两步加前面的检查，同步阶段总计40ms。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T25ms",
        "wallet balance check",
        "reserve funds",
        "CloudNative_ServiceMesh",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "Total sync: 40ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。T25ms节点包含12ms余额检查和15ms资金预留，标注了对应的云原生组件。然后T50ms发送响应给用户，加上10ms网络延迟，T60ms用户看到交易ID和成功状态，这里标记为Serverless。",
